Oh!

1102
01:09:04,958 --> 01:09:07,208
- Mrs. Dahlbeck.
- One point.

1103
01:09:07,291 --> 01:09:08,291
It's Bernard.

1104
01:09:11,041 --> 01:09:12,291
Francine's boy.

1105
01:09:13,166 --> 01:09:15,208
- Son, not boy.
- Shh.

1106
01:09:17,833 --> 01:09:20,750
