1111
01:09:36,166 --> 01:09:38,000
Oh, no, no.

1112
01:09:38,583 --> 01:09:42,125
Oh, no, no. No, no.
It-It's nothing important. I, um…

1113
01:09:45,708 --> 01:09:47,458
